<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>{{ title }}</title>
	<link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
	<link rel='stylesheet' href='/javascripts/highlight/styles/agate.css' />
	<script src="/javascripts/highlight/highlight.pack.js" />
	<script type="text/javascript">
	hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();
	</script>
</head>
<body class="wrapper">
	<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
	<p>Welcome to {{ title }}</p>
	<h2>You can do the following requests:</h2>
	<p>List all players in the Premier League</p>
	<pre>
		<code class="js hljs">/players/</code>
	</pre>
	<p>Search for specific player in the Premier League</p>
	<pre>
		<code class="js hljs">/players/{(surname)} //e.g /players/cech</code>
	</pre>
	<p>List all teams in the Permier League</p>
	<pre>
		<code class="js hljs">/team/</code>
	</pre>
	<p>List all players for a specific team in the Premier League</p>
	<pre>
		<code class="js hljs">/team/{(team)} //e.g /team/arsenal</code>
	</pre>
</body>
</html>